To generate Extended Data Figure 1a we downloaded the TAD positions in NPCs from Bonev et al. 2017.
Differentially expressed genes between ESC wt and NPC wt used in "4-gene_lengths_with_log2FC_TAD_annotation_and_nr_of_genes_in_TADs.tsv" are available in Supplementary Table 2, Sheet 3.
"Input for panelB" file was generated by extracting the %, and mean values of different categories from "4-gene_lengths_with_log2FC_TAD_annotation_and_nr_of_genes_in_TADs.tsv" file.
